data.text:
Berlin, Germany. 27th Jan, 2023. A tamping machine compacts ballast in the track bed during a site inspection of the north-south tunnel of the Berlin S-Bahn between the Oranienburger Strasse and Friedrichstrasse S-Bahn stations. Several S-Bahn lines will be interrupted for several weeks for maintenance and modernization work. Credit: Christoph Soeder/dpa/Alamy Live News
